%YAML 1.1
%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 9e7c527a6f66a8c49a6fab10a94681fc, type: 3}
  m_Name: Day4MorningN
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  sequenceId: albert_day4_morning_nopill
  lines:
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Morning, Andy. DOLOS has you at the server room today. The circuit box
      over there short-circuited last night.
    sendDelay: 0
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 1
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Most likely the result of a corporate attack from a rival company. All
      systems are nominal, per regular system reboots.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 2
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: All the circuit box needs is a full diagnostic check and some rewiring.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: Understood. Will get those wires all sorted in no time.
      nextLineIndex: 3
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: Feels like the DOLOS Corporation is always under a cyberattack
        every month.
      nextLineIndex: 4
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: Rival company? Which one?
      nextLineIndex: 6
      offPillChoice: 1
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: We could always count on you. Keep up that work ethic. The higher-ups love
      to see it.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 8
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "We expect it. Even before Erebus Holdings bought it, it was a common occurrence.
      But we always pull through\u2026 in one way, shape, or form."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 5
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Anyhow, do your job well.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 8
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Ethax Enterprise. A medium-sized conglomerate based in the North of the
      United Kingdom, specializing in pharmaceutical production and distribution.
      No need to worry about them; the DOLOS Corporation will take care of that issue
      promptly.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 2
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: How so?
      nextLineIndex: 7
      offPillChoice: 1
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "\u2026You don\u2019t have to worry about that."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 8
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Before you head out\u2026 you\u2019ve seemed different lately. Anything
      you wanna talk about?"
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices:
    - choiceText: "Just paying more attention. That\u2019s allowed, isn\u2019t it?"
      nextLineIndex: 9
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: "I feel like I\u2019m being watched. More than usual. Like the
        whole ship is watching me. Something\u2019s off\u2026"
      nextLineIndex: 10
      offPillChoice: 1
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: Can I ask you something personal?
      nextLineIndex: 17
      offPillChoice: 1
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: I gotta complete my shift now. Catch you later, Al.
      nextLineIndex: 23
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 1
    advanceToLine: 23
    repeat: 1
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "\u2026Of course. As long as it doesn\u2019t hinder your performance as
      a technician. Doing the tasks DOLOS assigns you is a part of your contract.
      Be sure not to breach its terms of service."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: I know that much.
      nextLineIndex: 8
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Really? It doesn\u2019t feel like that to me. I feel like you\u2019re
      just imagining things."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 11
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Are you getting enough sleep, Andy?
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 12
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Are the capsule injections not potent enough? Taking some extra dosages
      might alleviate the anxiety you\u2019re feeling."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 13
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Do you want me to report this to DOLOS?
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: "No, no. I\u2019m fine."
      nextLineIndex: 14
      offPillChoice: 1
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "I will say this: space has a way of bringing up thoughts you don\u2019t
      like if you let it happen\u2026"
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: "Yeah, you\u2019re right\u2026"
      nextLineIndex: 15
      offPillChoice: 1
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: "I\u2019m well aware, Al. There\u2019s no need to remind me."
      nextLineIndex: 16
      offPillChoice: 1
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "It\u2019s better to push those thoughts down by doing your tasks. Besides,
      doing your tasks keeps DOLOS happy."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.01
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 8
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Just looking out for ya, Andy.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.01
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 8
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Sure. What\u2019s on your mind?"
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: Did you have anyone down there? On Earth? A family, perhaps?
      nextLineIndex: 18
      offPillChoice: 1
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: '*&^&$#&#@'
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 19
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 1
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: I had a daughter. But that was a long time ago. I work here now. Doing
      my job here for DOLOS and the rest of the corporation is what matters.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 2
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 20
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Tell me, why are you thinking about that? I thought you hated Earth.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: "Nostalgia. That\u2019s all."
      nextLineIndex: 21
      offPillChoice: 1
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: "Just\u2026 thinking about someone."
      nextLineIndex: 22
      offPillChoice: 1
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Are you sure?
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: "Yeah, I\u2019m sure\u2026"
      nextLineIndex: 8
      offPillChoice: 1
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "It happens. But there\u2019s a reason why you\u2019re here, and on this
      ship. Don\u2019t let those memories distract you from your assignments. Those
      capsules should take care of that issue for you."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.01
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 8
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Talk to you later then, Andy.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: -1
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
